title: Open Bar #31 - Witcher Blood Origin Flop, Best And Worst Of 2022
description:
Well, this is it. The last few days of the year. Join me, Longman, Nerdrotic, Geeks + Gamers and Metalcommander as we look back on the highs and lows of 2022. Oh, and have a good laugh at Witcher: Blood Origin.
